### `admins` table
| Column | Type | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| [id](file:///c:/Users/Haram/Desktop/rac%20clone/src/components/BenefitGrid.tsx#37-73) | INTEGER (PK, auto) | |
| `username` | TEXT (unique) | |
