### API Routes

#### [NEW] [route.ts](file:///c:/Users/Haram/Desktop/rac%20clone/src/app/api/admin/login/route.ts)
- `POST /api/admin/login` — validate credentials, set auth cookie, return admin info

#### [NEW] [route.ts](file:///c:/Users/Haram/Desktop/rac%20clone/src/app/api/admin/logout/route.ts)
- `POST /api/admin/logout` — clear auth cookie

#### [NEW] [route.ts](file:///c:/Users/Haram/Desktop/rac%20clone/src/app/api/policies/route.ts)
- `POST /api/policies` — create new policy, generate policy number, send email, return created policy
