#### [NEW] [route.ts](file:///c:/Users/Haram/Desktop/rac%20clone/src/app/api/retrieve/route.ts)
- `POST /api/retrieve` — lookup policy by surname + DOB + postcode, return policy details

#### [NEW] [route.ts](file:///c:/Users/Haram/Desktop/rac%20clone/src/app/api/admin/stats/route.ts)
- `GET /api/admin/stats` — return counts (total accounts, active policies, etc.)

